\id JON - Aboriginal Plain English Version 
\h Jonah 
\toc3 Jonah 
\toc2 Jonah 
\toc1 The Book of Jonah 
\mt1 The story about Jonah  
\mt2 (The book in the Holy Bible called \bk Jonah\bk*)  
\imt1 About this story  
\ip This story is about a man called Jonah. He lived about 800 years before Jesus came to earth.  
\ip This story was in God’s book that the Israel people had before Jesus came to earth. That book is now the first part of the Holy Bible, called the Old Testament.  
\ip Jonah was a man that God picked to tell people his messages. Back then, God normally just told his own Israel people his messages, he didn’t normally tell messages to other nations. But the story of Jonah is different. Jonah lived in Israel country, but God sent him to a big city called Nineveh, that was not in Israel country. Nineveh was in a country called Assyria, and the people from Nineveh were enemies of God’s Israel people. God sent Jonah to Nineveh to tell the Nineveh people his message.  
\ip At first, Jonah didn’t listen to God. He tried to run away from God. But God still wanted to use Jonah to tell the Nineveh people his message. So God talked to Jonah again.  
\ip This story happened a long time ago, but it is still very important for us today. It shows us that God uses his people to share his messages. And it shows us that God cares about people, and that everyone needs to hear God’s message. And it shows us that sometimes bad people listen to God, and they tell him they are sorry, and they stop living the wrong way. And then God feels sorry for them, and he doesn’t punish them. He lets go of all the bad things that they did, and he is very good to them.  
\c 1  
\s1 Jonah ran away from God  
\p
\v 1 \w There|strong="H1961"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w in|strong="H3068"\w* Israel country called \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w*. \w His|strong="H3068"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w*’s name \w was|strong="H3068"\w* Amittai. \w One|strong="H1121"\w* day, \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Israel talked \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w*.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Kings 14:25\x* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w*,  
\v 2 “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* know \w the|strong="H6440"\w* big \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w Nineveh|strong="H5210"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H5892"\w* \w not|strong="H3588"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* Israel country? \w The|strong="H6440"\w* people \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* do really \w bad|strong="H7451"\w* \w things|strong="H1419"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* see \w all|strong="H1419"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w things|strong="H1419"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* do. \w So|strong="H7121"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H5892"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w go|strong="H3212"\w* \w there|strong="H5927"\w* \w now|strong="H3588"\w*, \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* big \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w Nineveh|strong="H5210"\w*. \w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H5892"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* tell \w those|strong="H5921"\w* people, ‘God \w is|strong="H5892"\w* angry \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*.’”   
\p
\v 3 \w But|strong="H3068"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w* didn’t listen \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. Instead, \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w ran|strong="H1272"\w* \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w went|strong="H3381"\w* \w down|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* town called \w Joppa|strong="H3305"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w get|strong="H6965"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* ship \w there|strong="H4672"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w go|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* town called \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w*. \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w long|strong="H6440"\w* \w way|strong="H6440"\w* \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* Nineveh. \fig Jonah ran away from God and got on a ship|src="lll5-07.jpg" size="col" ref="1:3" \fig*  
\p \w In|strong="H3068"\w* \w Joppa|strong="H3305"\w*, \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w* \w found|strong="H4672"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* ship \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w going|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w*, \w so|strong="H5414"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w paid|strong="H5414"\w* some money \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* ship-men \w so|strong="H5414"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* can \w go|strong="H3381"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* ship. \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* ship \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w go|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w*. \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* running \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*.   
\p
\v 4-5 Then Jonah went down inside the ship and lay down, and he fell asleep.  
\p While they were sailing, God sent \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big wind over the sea, and there was \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big storm.\fig There was a big storm and the ship-men were frightened|src="AP-04-02c - edited.jpg" size="col" ref="1:4-5" \fig* That storm was really strong, and the ship-men thought the ship might break up. All the ship-men were frightened, so they called out to their own gods and asked them to help.  
\p That ship was carrying lots of heavy boxes and bags of things, to take them to Tarshish. But that storm was really big, so the ship-men threw all those heavy things into the sea to make the ship lighter. \fig The ship-men threw all the heavy boxes and bags into the sea|src="Bible1085 - edited.jpg" size="col" ref="1:4-5" \fig*   
\p
\v 6 Jonah \w was|strong="H3808"\w* still \w asleep|strong="H7290"\w* \w down|strong="H7121"\w* inside \w the|strong="H7121"\w* ship, \w so|strong="H7121"\w* \w the|strong="H7121"\w* ship’s boss \w went|strong="H7126"\w* \w to|strong="H6965"\w* Jonah \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w are|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H3808"\w* \w sleeping|strong="H7290"\w*? \w Get|strong="H6965"\w* \w up|strong="H6965"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w pray|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H6965"\w* \w your|strong="H3808"\w* \w god|strong="H3808"\w*. Maybe \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* feel sorry \w for|strong="H7121"\w* \w us|strong="H7121"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w help|strong="H6965"\w* \w us|strong="H7121"\w*, \w so|strong="H7121"\w* \w that|strong="H7121"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* don’t die.”   
\p
\v 7 \w Then|strong="H5307"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ship-men talked \w to|strong="H3212"\w* each \w other|strong="H7453"\w*. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* said, “\w Why|strong="H5921"\w* \w do|strong="H4310"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* \w trouble|strong="H7451"\w*? \w Who|strong="H4310"\w* \w did|strong="H5307"\w* something \w wrong|strong="H7451"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w make|strong="H3045"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* \w trouble|strong="H7451"\w* \w come|strong="H3212"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*? \w Let|strong="H3212"\w*’s put small stones \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bag, \w one|strong="H7453"\w* stone \w for|strong="H5921"\w* each \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w*’ll pull \w out|strong="H5921"\w* \w one|strong="H7453"\w* \w person|strong="H3045"\w*’s stone. \w That|strong="H3045"\w* stone \w will|strong="H4310"\w* \w show|strong="H3045"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w* \w who|strong="H4310"\w* \w made|strong="H3045"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* \w trouble|strong="H7451"\w* \w come|strong="H3212"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*.” \w So|strong="H2063"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w did|strong="H5307"\w* \w that|strong="H3045"\w*, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* pulled \w out|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w*’s stone. \fig The sailors pulled out Jonah’s stone, so they knew that the storm was Jonah’s fault|src="GT Jonah Sailors cast lots.tif" size="col" ref="1:7" \fig*   
\p
\v 8 \w So|strong="H2088"\w* \w those|strong="H2063"\w* ship-men \w asked|strong="H4100"\w* Jonah, “\w Did|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H5046"\w* \w make|strong="H5046"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w trouble|strong="H7451"\w* \w come|strong="H4994"\w* \w on|strong="H4399"\w* \w us|strong="H4994"\w*? \w Did|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H5046"\w* \w do|strong="H4100"\w* \w something|strong="H4399"\w* \w bad|strong="H7451"\w*? \w Who|strong="H4310"\w* \w are|strong="H5971"\w* \w you|strong="H5046"\w*? \w What|strong="H4100"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w your|strong="H4994"\w* job? \w And|strong="H5971"\w* \w where|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H5046"\w* \w come|strong="H4994"\w* \w from|strong="H7451"\w*? \w What|strong="H4100"\w* country \w are|strong="H5971"\w* \w you|strong="H5046"\w* \w from|strong="H7451"\w*? \w And|strong="H5971"\w* \w who|strong="H4310"\w* \w are|strong="H5971"\w* \w your|strong="H4994"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w*?”   
\p
\v 9 Jonah said \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w*, “\w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w Hebrew|strong="H5680"\w* people, \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w Israel|strong="H8064"\w* country. \w Our|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*’s name \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* respect \w him|strong="H6213"\w*. \w I|strong="H3068"\w* know \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* power. \w He|strong="H6213"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* big boss \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8064"\w*. \w He|strong="H6213"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w land|strong="H3004"\w*.  
\v 10 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w right|strong="H3068"\w* \w now|strong="H3588"\w*, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w am|strong="H3068"\w* running \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*.”  
\p \w Then|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* ship-men got \w really|strong="H1992"\w* \w frightened|strong="H3372"\w*. \w They|strong="H1992"\w* \w asked|strong="H4100"\w* Jonah, “\w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w are|strong="H1992"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* running \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w god|strong="H3068"\w*? \w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bad \w thing|strong="H2063"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*.”   
\p
\v 11 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w was|strong="H3220"\w* getting \w more|strong="H3588"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w more|strong="H3588"\w* rough. \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ship-men \w asked|strong="H4100"\w* Jonah, “\w How|strong="H4100"\w* \w can|strong="H4100"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* stop \w this|strong="H6213"\w* \w storm|strong="H5590"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w quiet|strong="H8367"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w still|strong="H1980"\w*? \w What|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*?”   
\p
\v 12 Jonah said \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w pick|strong="H5375"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w throw|strong="H2904"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w into|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*. \w Then|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w storm|strong="H5591"\w* \w will|strong="H7945"\w* stop, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w will|strong="H7945"\w* \w be|strong="H5375"\w* \w quiet|strong="H8367"\w* \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w still|strong="H3588"\w*. \w This|strong="H2088"\w* \w storm|strong="H5591"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* fault. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* did something wrong, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w*’s \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w reason|strong="H5921"\w* \w why|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H3045"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* big \w storm|strong="H5591"\w*.”   
\p
\v 13 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ship-men didn’t \w want|strong="H3808"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* throw Jonah \w into|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*, \w so|strong="H1980"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* tried \w hard|strong="H2864"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* row \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w land|strong="H3004"\w*. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w was|strong="H3220"\w* getting \w more|strong="H3808"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w more|strong="H3808"\w* rough, \w so|strong="H1980"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* couldn’t \w do|strong="H3201"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w*.   
\p
\v 14 \w Then|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* ship-men \w prayed|strong="H7121"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* Jonah’s \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. \w They|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w sent|strong="H5414"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* storm \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w happen|strong="H6213"\w*. \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* throw \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w man|strong="H5315"\w* \w into|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sea, \w please|strong="H4994"\w* don’t kill \w us|strong="H5414"\w*. Maybe \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* nothing wrong, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* don’t know, \w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w please|strong="H4994"\w* don’t \w do|strong="H6213"\w* payback \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w us|strong="H5414"\w*.”   
\p
\v 15 \w Then|strong="H5375"\w* \w they|strong="H5375"\w* \w picked|strong="H5375"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w*, \w and|strong="H5975"\w* \w they|strong="H5375"\w* \w threw|strong="H2904"\w* \w him|strong="H5975"\w* \w into|strong="H3220"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*, \w and|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* storm \w stopped|strong="H5975"\w*, \w and|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H5375"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w was|strong="H3220"\w* quiet \w and|strong="H5975"\w* \w still|strong="H5975"\w*. \fig The ship-men threw Jonah into the sea|src="AP-04-07c - edited.jpg" size="col" ref="1:15" \fig*   
\p
\v 16 \w Then|strong="H3372"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* ship-men knew \w that|strong="H3068"\w* Jonah’s \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* powerful, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w showed|strong="H3372"\w* \w him|strong="H3372"\w* lots \w of|strong="H3068"\w* respect. \w They|strong="H3068"\w* \w killed|strong="H2076"\w* \w an|strong="H3068"\w* animal \w to|strong="H3068"\w* give \w to|strong="H3068"\w* Jonah’s \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H5087"\w* promises \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H3372"\w*.   
\s1 God sent a big fish to Jonah  
\p
\v 17 While the ship-men did that, God sent \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big fish to Jonah. Jonah was deep down in the water, and that big fish came and swallowed Jonah alive. Jonah stayed inside that fish for 3 days and 3 nights.\x * \xo 1:17 \xt Matthew 12:40\x*\fig Jonah was deep down in the water, and God sent a big fish|src="GT Jonah in the deep.tif" size="col" ref="1:17" \fig*   
\c 2  
\s1 Jonah prayed to God  
\p
\v 1 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w Jonah|strong="H3124"\w* prayed \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w from|strong="H3117"\w* \w inside|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w fish|strong="H1709"\w*. \w He|strong="H3117"\w* talked \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w things|strong="H1419"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w happened|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H3117"\w* \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* water \w before|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w fish|strong="H1709"\w* \w came|strong="H1961"\w*.   
\m
\v 2 \w He|strong="H3068"\w* said,  
\q1 “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w when|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* got trouble, \w I|strong="H3068"\w* called out \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6419"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6419"\w* answered me.  
\q2 \w I|strong="H3068"\w* nearly died, \w but|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* called out \w for|strong="H3068"\w* help, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6419"\w* listened \w to|strong="H3068"\w* me.   
\q1
\v 3 \w This|strong="H7121"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w what|strong="H6963"\w* happened.  
\q1 First \w you|strong="H6963"\w* \w made|strong="H7121"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w* \w go|strong="H3068"\w* \w down|strong="H7121"\w* into deep \w water|strong="H7121"\w*, into \w the|strong="H8085"\w* middle \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* sea.  
\q2 \w The|strong="H8085"\w* \w water|strong="H7121"\w* moved \w all|strong="H7121"\w* around \w me|strong="H7121"\w*. \w You|strong="H6963"\w* \w sent|strong="H3068"\w* big waves \w over|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w*.   
\q1
\v 4 \w I|strong="H5921"\w* knew \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w sent|strong="H5674"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w away|strong="H5674"\w*. \w You|strong="H3605"\w* didn’t want \w to|strong="H5921"\w* look \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w any|strong="H3605"\w* \w more|strong="H5921"\w*.  
